					<p class="txt-lrg">A collective of like-minded web designers, developers, SEO, and social media marketing professionals with a diverse range of expertise and backgrounds.</p>
					<p>service, turnaround times</p>
				</div>
				<div class="cell shrink">
					<Picture src={jeff} class="ai-card-img" alt="Jeff" />
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex padding-x align-middle person">
				<div class="cell shrink">
					<Picture src={jeff} class="ai-card-img" alt="Jeff" />
				</div>
				<div class="cell auto">
					<h2 class="title">Jeff McKean</h2>
					<h3 class="sub-title">Web Developer</h3>
					<p class="txt-lrg">Jeff has a background in Web design and multimedia and extensive experience in building brochure sites for lead capturing and...</p>
